            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Rear disc brake caliper</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Rear disc brake rotor and hub assembly</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Rear disc brake caliper anchor plate</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Brake pads</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Brake caliper support bracket</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <para>The rear disc brake has the following characteristics:</para>
        <randlist type="bullet">
            <item>
                <para>A 2-piston rear disc brake caliper</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>A vented-cast, drum-in-hat type rear disc brake rotor</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>A rear disc brake caliper anchor holds the brake pads</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>A rear wheel drum-in-hat adapter holds the rear disc brake caliper anchor and the rear wheel disc
                    brake shield
                </para>
            </item>
        </randlist>
    </svcproc>
